description: Entourage Health Corp. engages in the production and distribution of cannabis products for medical and adult-use markets in Canada. The company offers cannabis plants, dried cannabis, oils, topicals, extracts, and edibles. It provides its products under the Color Cannabis, Saturday Cannabis, Starseed Medicinals, and Mary's Medicinals brand names. The company was formerly known as WeedMD Inc. and changed its name to Entourage Health Corp. in July 2021. Entourage Health Corp. is headquartered in Toronto, Canada.
